{"title":"真话与假话","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":250,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1857","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span>一次考试共有</span><span>n</span><span>个人参加，第</span><span>i</span><span>个人说：“有</span><span>ai</span><span>个人分数比我高，</span><span>bi</span><span>个人分数比我低。”问最少有几个人没有说真话</span><span>(</span><span>可能有相同的分数</span><span>)</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>第一行一个整数</span><span>n</span><span>，接下来</span><span>n</span><span>行每行两个整数，第</span><span>i+1</span><span>行的两个整数分别代表</span><span>ai</span><span>、</span><span>bi</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span>一个整数，表示最少有几个人说谎</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>3</span><br><br><span> 2 0</span><br><br><span> 0 2</span><br><br><span> 2 2</span><br><br><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>1</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span>100%的数据满足： 1≤n≤100000   0≤ai、bi≤n</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}